Linux FTP comands
-------------------
rpm -qa |grep vsftpd
systemctl status vsftpd
systemctl enable vsftpd
firewall-cmd --list-all
  


 #start configuration
 ----------------------
 mkdir /ftp-dir
 chmod 777 /ftp   -dir
cd /ftp-dir/
touch file1 file2 file3
cd 
#

Ftp installation
-----------------
yum install ftp -y
